              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4246571-laura?shelf=france">france</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer450798871" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1553370997970737555">Although written by a journalist rather than a historian, this hefty book does a great job of making history come alive -- in terms of both characters and events. His see-it-now coverage of the making of the Nazi machine is priceless. I wish that schools used books like this rather than the dry, dull textbooks that put us all to sleep!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


